            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mt-4">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold mt-1">&#10003;</span>
                <span><strong>Entertainment Centers & Media Walls</strong> — Floor-to-ceiling built-in units with integrated cable management, adjustable shelving, and soft-close doors. From $1,200 to $4,000+ depending on size and complexity.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold mt-1">&#10003;</span>
                <span><strong>Fireplace Mantels & Surrounds</strong> — Hand-crafted mantels in solid hardwood with custom molding profiles. We design around your firebox dimensions for a perfect, code-compliant fit.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold mt-1">&#10003;</span>
                <span><strong>Crown Molding & Trim</strong> — Custom-profiled crown, baseboards, casing, and chair rail in solid wood. We mill unique profiles to match existing trim or create something entirely new.</span>
              </li>
