                <span><strong>Wainscoting & Wall Paneling</strong> — Raised panel, shaker, and board-and-batten wainscoting that adds architectural character to dining rooms, hallways, and staircases.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold mt-1">&#10003;</span>
                <span><strong>Built-In Bookshelves & Home Offices</strong> — Custom shelving and desk units built into alcoves, under stairs, or across entire walls. Finished to match your existing home woodwork.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold mt-1">&#10003;</span>
                <span><strong>Custom Closet Systems</strong> — Walk-in closet built-ins from real wood with dovetailed drawers, soft-close slides, and adjustable hanging rods. No wire racks, no particle board.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="reveal bg-zinc-50 p-8 rounded-sm border border-zinc-100">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6 text-center">Custom Woodworker vs. Handyman</h3>
