                  <tr><td class="py-4 font-bold">Custom Fit</td><td class="py-4 text-zinc-500">Shimmed and caulked to fit</td><td class="py-4 font-bold text-zinc-900">Scribed to walls, precision-fit</td></tr>
                  <tr><td class="py-4 font-bold">Design</td><td class="py-4 text-zinc-500">No renderings — "trust me"</td><td class="py-4 font-bold text-zinc-900">Full 3D renderings before build</td></tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="reveal">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4">Our Woodworking Process</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6 mt-6">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-serif text-2xl font-bold">1.</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-bold text-zinc-900">In-Home Design Consultation</p>
                  <p>We visit your home in Murrieta, Temecula, or anywhere in the Temecula Valley. We measure the space, discuss your vision, and review wood species, stain samples, and hardware options.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-serif text-2xl font-bold">2.</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-bold text-zinc-900">3D Design & Approval</p>
                  <p>We create detailed 3D renderings so you see the finished product before we start building. You approve every dimension, every profile, and every finish detail.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-serif text-2xl font-bold">3.</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-bold text-zinc-900">In-Shop Craftsmanship</p>
                  <p>Every component is built by our own craftsmen. Dovetailed drawers, mortise-and-tenon frames, and post-catalyzed conversion varnish — applied in controlled shop conditions for a flawless cure.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 font-serif text-2xl font-bold">4.</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-bold text-zinc-900">Professional Installation</p>
                  <p>Our team installs on-site with HEPA dust extraction and full floor protection. Built-ins are scribed to your walls for a seamless, custom-fitted result. Typical timeline: 8-12 weeks from design approval.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="reveal">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 pt-10 mb-6">Custom Woodworking FAQ</h3>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              {faqs.map((faq) => (
                <details class="group bg-zinc-50 border border-zinc-200 rounded-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all">
                  <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-6 list-none">
                    <h4 class="font-serif font-bold text-zinc-800 group-hover:text-yellow-600 transition-colors pr-8">
                      {faq.question}
                    </h4>
                    <span class="text-yellow-600 transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180 flex-shrink-0">
